name: RALKATH.WAD
description: Ok, this is a nice little replacement .EXE file for Doom 2. It changes some of the enemies into other players (just like the ones you kill in deathmatch). There are 4 different types of players, and here's the list! COLOUR WEAPON SPEED HEALTH Green Rocket Launcher Okay Good Indigo Shotgun Okay Okay Brown Pistol Bad Okay Red Chaingun Good Bad
